          <p data-propname="parts.1.worked_solutions.1.text">
            <!-- CHANGE WORKED SOLUTIONS TEXT HERE -->
            For CO2 in air \(D=1.37\times10^{-5}m^{2}/s\). If \(\sigma=\sqrt{2Dt}\) then \(t=\frac{\sigma^{2}}{2D}\), and one must wait \(t=10^{2}/(2\times1.37\times10^{-5})=36500000\) s=42days.
          </p>
        </div>
